kbd-auto-layout (1.0.8) stable; urgency=medium

  * Add configurable XKB apply retries and retry delay.
  * Re-apply active layout when current XKB state diverges.
  * Add rules command and support removing rules by index.
  * Improve doctor output for Wayland sessions.
  * Add regression tests for startup layout application.

